<darktable_style version="1.0"><info><name>look_wildlife_eye_lift</name><description>Catchlight emphasis on the wildlife subject's eye — exposure +0.3 EV + sharpen amount 1.5, scoped to mask_eye_region (RFC-032). The eye becomes the brightest, sharpest point in the frame; gives the bird / animal its 'life.' Cross-genre echo of Portrait Move 7 (eye-detail lift). For close-up wildlife where the subject's gaze is the picture.</description><iop_list>colorin,demosaic,temperature,exposure,colorbalancergb,bilat,grain,sigmoid,colorout,sharpen</iop_list></info><style><plugin><num>10</num><module>7</module><operation>exposure</operation><op_params>00000000000080b99a99993e00004842000080c00100000001000000</op_params><enabled>1</enabled><blendop_params>gz08eJxjYGBgYAFiCQYYOOHEgAZY0QWAgBGLGANDgz0Ej1Q+dlAx68oBEMbFxwX+AwGIBgCbGCeh</blendop_params><blendop_version>14</blendop_version><multi_priority>0</multi_priority><multi_name></multi_name><multi_name_hand_edited>0</multi_name_hand_edited></plugin><plugin><num>11</num><module>10</module><operation>sharpen</operation><op_params>000000400000c03f0000003f</op_params><enabled>1</enabled><blendop_params>gz08eJxjYGBgYAFiCQYYOOHEgAZY0QWAgBGLGANDgz0Ej1Q+dlAx68oBEMbFxwX+AwGIBgCbGCeh</blendop_params><blendop_version>14</blendop_version><multi_priority>0</multi_priority><multi_name></multi_name><multi_name_hand_edited>0</multi_name_hand_edited></plugin></style></darktable_style>
